{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Trailer Venom Rilis, Fans Menanyakan Keberadaan Spider-Man!","content":"<p>Kamu sudah lihat trailer film Venom dari Sony Pictures dong?</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/dzxFdtWmjto\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Film yang dibintangi oleh <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/tom-hardy-beberkan-cerita-lain-musuh-spider-man-di-brazil-comic-con/\">Tom Hardy</a> ini menarik perhatian karena beberapa faktor.</p>\n<p>Seperti misalnya faktor Tom Hardy sendiri. Venom bukan film pertama Hardy di genre ‘comicbook superheroes movie’. Sebelumnya dia memerankan karakter antagonis populer dari DC Universe ‘Bane’ di film “The Dark Knight Rises” (2012). Hardy juga berperan di film remake Mad Max (yang dulu dipopulerkan Mel Gibson) “Mad Max: Fury Road” (2015). Mad Max memang bukan karakter dari komik asli, tapi dia menginspirasi karakter komik Jepang <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/fist-north-star-girls-last-tour-dua-pendekatan-berbeda-untuk-kisah-dunia-post-apocalyptic/\">“Hokuto no Ken”</a> yang fenomenal.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47038\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47038\" data-attachment-id=\"47038\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/01-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47038\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-venom.jpg\" alt=\"01 venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/01-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47038\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tom Hardy sebagai Bane di film “The Dark Knight Rises”. Sumber: Nerdist</p></div></p>\n<p>Mungkin hal-hal itu yang mendasari pemilihan Tom Hardy sebagai Venom di film buatan Sony Pictures ini?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47039\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47039\" data-attachment-id=\"47039\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/02-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47039\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-venom.jpg\" alt=\"02-venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/02-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47039\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: GameSpot</p></div></p>\n<p>Sony Pictures memiliki hak untuk membuat film-film dengan karakter dari komik Marvel “Spider-Man”. Marvel Studios tidak punya hak tersebut. Mengapa?</p>\n<p>Karena dulu Sony Pictures membeli hak pembuatan film Spider-Man (dan karakter-karakter yang berhubungan dengan Spider-Man) dari Marvel Comics sebelum kemudian Marvel dibeli oleh Disney. Jadi jika Disney/Marvel Studios mau memakai karakter dari <em>lore/universe</em>  Spider-Man mereka harus permisi (dan bayar) kepada Sony. Itu terlihat di film “Spider-Man: Homecoming” dan “The Avengers: Infinity War” buatan Marvel Studios; dimana karakter Spider-Man ada disana karena adanya ijin khusus dari Sony Pictures.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47040\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47040\" data-attachment-id=\"47040\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/03-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47040\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-venom.jpg\" alt=\"03-venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/03-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47040\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Film-film Spider-Man merupakan milik Sony Pictures. Sumber: ThePolitic.Org</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan pembuatan film “Venom”, Sony seakan sedang berusaha membuat “Marvel Cinematic Universe” versi mereka sendiri. Terpisah dari MCU Marvel Studios . Dengan karakter Marvel yang mereka miliki hak nya.</p>\n<p>Mungkin tidak akan semudah yang mereka bayangkan. Apalagi saat melihat trailer terkini Venom yang sudah beredar di YouTube itu.</p>\n<p>Ada yang belum familiar dengan Venom?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47041\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47041\" data-attachment-id=\"47041\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/04-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47041\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-venom.jpg\" alt=\"04-venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/04-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47041\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: AnEnglishmanInSanDiego</p></div></p>\n<p>Di film, penampilan perdana dia ada di film Sony Pictures “Spider-Man 3” (2007) dan diperankan oleh aktor Topher Grace. Sementara di komik, Venom muncul pertama kali di komik “The Amazing Spider-Man” #252 (bulan Mei tahun 1984). Jadi versi komik lahir lebih awal dan secara <em>default</em> menjadi sumber utama kisah <em>origins</em> dari karakter <em>villain</em> ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47042\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47042\" data-attachment-id=\"47042\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/05-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47042\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-venom.jpg\" alt=\"05-venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/05-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47042\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Topher Grace di “Spider-Man 3”. Sumber: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Di komik, Venom adalah “Symbiote”; alien berbentuk cairan bersifat parasit yang memerlukan <em>host</em>/inang untuk bertahan hidup. Saat bersatu dengan <em>host,</em> Symbiote ini selain memiliki kekuatan super (yang disalurkan ke <em>host</em>) juga memiliki kesadarannya sendiri sehingga terjadi dualisme jiwa di satu raga. Symbiote menamai dirinya sebagai Venom.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47043\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47043\" data-attachment-id=\"47043\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/06-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47043\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-venom.jpg\" alt=\"06-venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/06-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47043\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Cikal bakal kelahiran Venom. Sumber: Wikia</p></div></p>\n<p>Inang dari Symbiote pertama di Bumi adalah Peter Parker/Spider-Man; seperti yang terlihat di komik “The Amazing Spider-Man” #252.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47044\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47044\" data-attachment-id=\"47044\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/07-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47044\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-venom.jpg\" alt=\"07-venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/07-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47044\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Konflik internal. Sumber: 4thletter</p></div></p>\n<p>Namun itu tidak berlangsung lama karena Parker menyadari kalau Symbiote ini memiliki sifat kejahatan yang berlawanan dengan prinsip yang dia jalankan. Spider-Man menyingkirkan Symbiote tersebut, namun sang Symbiote segera mencari pengganti Parker dan menemukannya pada sosok Eddie Brock; wartawan investigasi saingan Peter Parker. Brock sendiri sebelum menjadi Venom memang menyimpan kebencian pada Spider-Man (dan Peter Parker) sehingga Symbiote dengan mudah mempengaruhi dirinya. Venom lahir dan menyebabkan kehidupan Spider-Man/Peter Parker bagaikan neraka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_47045\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-47045\" data-attachment-id=\"47045\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/trailer-venom-keberadaan-spider-man/attachment/08-venom/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/08-venom.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-venom\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/08-venom-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/08-venom.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-47045\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/08-venom.jpg\" alt=\"08-venom\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/08-venom.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/08-venom-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-47045\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Musuh bebuyutan. Sumber: 4thletter</p></div></p>\n<p>Dengan <em>origins</em> seperti itu, jelas Venom (dan Eddie Brock) punya hubungan erat satu sama lain. Di film Spider-Man 3 <em>origins</em> ini diceritakan ulang dengan cukup akurat sehingga walaupun Topher Grace tidak terlalu mengesankan saat berakting sebagai Eddie Brock / Venom tapi masih dapat diterima oleh fans Spider-Man dan Venom.</p>\n<p>Situasi ini tidak terjadi di film-nya Tom Hardy.</p>\n<p>Walau masih dalam format trailer (film-nya sendiri baru akan dirilis 5 Oktober 2018) namun suara-suara ketidakpuasan sudah terdengar di internet. Dan itu jadi terasa wajar karena di trailer yang ada, Spider-Man sama sekali tidak terlihat sedetik pun.</p>\n<p>Symbiote jelas ada di trailer; dimana itupun salah diucapkan menurut fans-fans garis keras Marvel (karena penyebutannya seharusnya ‘simbiot’ dan bukannya ‘simbayot’ seperti yang terdengar di trailer). Tom Hardy sebagai Eddie Brock terlihat lumayan meyakinkan karena tongkrongannya yang memang <em>intimidating</em> ketimbang Topher Grace di Spider-Man 3. Tapi faktor penting eksistensi Venom sejak awal kelahirannya malah tidak terlihat; yaitu keberadaan Spider-Man.</p>\n<p>Untuk saat ini, film “Venom” dari Sony Pictures lebih mirip film monster/alien yang menginvasi seseorang (yang tidak memiliki sifat heroik) hingga orang ini mendapatkan kekuatan super. Venom memang seorang antihero (atau lebih cocok disebut supervillain?) dan karena itulah sosok penyeimbang alias superhero dibutuhkan. Sesuatu yang tidak terlihat di trailer film. Dan mungkin di film teatrikalnya Oktober nanti.</p>\n<p>Apakah memang Spider-Man tidak akan muncul? Kalau melihat ending “The Avengers: Infinity War” sih….. gimana ya….</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"bf15b768-57e2-57db-932a-20fce5e68c86"}}}